amarok (2:1.4.10-0ubuntu3~ppa4) jaunty; urgency=low

  * Fixes dependencies. Sorry for the mess with the last upload.

 -- Bogdan Butnaru <bogdanb@gmail.com>  Thu, 11 Jun 2009 01:54:27 +0200

